[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "像被凌空抽飞的棒球一样，罗赞被这一拳轰进了墙壁里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "利用对泰坦物质的新发现，打了罗赞一个措手不及。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "丧钟！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不假思索地冲了过去。不需要说更多，卜卜便紧跟在我的身后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“丧钟”的使用条件已经变得苛刻了。我必须在“丧钟”生效的瞬间和罗赞保持距离。否则，近距离的作战会使“丧钟”对罗赞的影响大幅度降低。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而罗赞拥有经过泰坦物质强化的防御能力，我又必须在“丧钟”单次生效的短暂的持续时间内，击杀罗赞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而如果选择撤下防御、和罗赞一同承受“丧钟”的影响，我也没有十足的把握在非常有限的时间内击杀罗赞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一旦“丧钟”的三次振荡波结束，罗赞就能通过泰坦物质修复身体，恢复所有伤势。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——但这也在我的预料之中。对于如何在与罗赞的争斗中取得胜势，我早有计划。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "镜爻的声音在身后响起，“丧钟”即将生效，我也已经到达了罗赞所在的墙壁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一道黑影出现在视野里。只来得及护住胸前，就被什么东西击中了——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗡——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这次轮到我，被罗赞蓄意的反击逼退了——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "退了好几步才卸掉所有的力量。糟糕的是，第一次“丧钟”已经生效了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了使丧钟的影响降到最低，在冲向罗赞时，并没有使用泰坦物质强化肌肉。而罗赞捕捉到了我的战斗意图，冒着被“丧钟”重创的风险，给了我一记重击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "停！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大厅两边的墙壁上各有一处蛛网状凹陷。我叫停了“丧钟”的下一次攻击，石块和泥灰还在落下，罗赞已经站在了我的对面。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她擦了擦血迹——她的口鼻以及眼角都有流出的鲜血。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想必是因为调动泰坦物质的力量攻击我，能量态的泰坦物质受“丧钟”的影响，让她受了严重的内伤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好魄力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我和卜卜、猫汐尔站在了一起。卜卜的镜爻刚刚被我撞散了，这会儿重新在我们的后方聚集，以作观察和屏卫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "罗赞",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_rozan_01",
        "zh_CN": "果然……我就知道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“呸”的一声，她吐了一口血到地上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "罗赞",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_rozan_02",
        "zh_CN": "你总能给我惊喜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_girl012_01",
        "zh_CN": "锁定爱思特的位置了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她是第一目标。你们也是罗赞的第一目标。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_girl020_01",
        "zh_CN": "明白！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我没理会自说自话的罗赞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周围的泰坦物质已经被清空，罗赞能使用的只有她体内储存的那些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只要消耗掉所有的泰坦物质，战斗自然就有结果了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞眯着眼睛看着我。双方都不愿意先动手——我不想放过这个击败她的机会，但她还留在这里的原因……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（……她还有后手吗？）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞往前走了一步，猫汐尔举起了手中的“丧钟”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还有两次使用“丧钟”的机会。我方的劣势在于，决定使用“丧钟”时机的人是我，而实际操纵“丧钟”的是猫汐尔。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "战场瞬息万变，机会稍纵即逝。在力量和速度都远超常人的战斗中，“丧钟”完全有可能被浪费掉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（那就先假定“丧钟”不存在。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我举起拳头，意念控制能量态的泰坦物质散入全身。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "运用这种技巧时，我的力量和速度犹在罗赞之上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 411.0,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但罗赞对这种技巧的理解比我更深——她几乎可以一直维持这种力量和速度，而我则需要一次又一次控制泰坦物质到达对应的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "爱思特也从阴影中现身了——我先看见的是她那双无神的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "像一团干枯的木头，又像一段干涸的河床。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但在眼神对上的一瞬间，在看见我的一瞬间——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "烈焰熊熊，波涛滚滚。她像是找到了存在于这个空间和时间的目的，找到了活着的信念和理由。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果说罗赞的眼中是冰冷、干净、纯粹的杀意，那爱思特的眼里则是复杂、浓重、浑浊的恨意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好像活着就是为了诞生这段仇恨，了结这段仇恨。自然而然地，压抑而不得释放的吼叫声回响在这片空间里——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "真神爱思特",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_esther_01",
        "zh_CN": "playername！！！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她就这么冲进我和罗赞的对峙中。对面的罗赞冷笑着，任由爱思特冲向蓄势待发的我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "显然是弃子。她丝毫不在意爱思特的生命——只要爱思特能为她赢得一丝先机，她便毫不犹豫地让爱思特去做。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "奔向死亡般的冲锋。全无防御，根本不考虑任何可能受到的伤害。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "连天启者都难以反应的速度和力量。像飞驰的载具一样，撞了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞在她身后动了。用爱思特遮掩着身形，如同举着盾牌和长枪的骑士，罗赞也冲了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只来得及回头看一眼——好在猫汐尔和卜卜都明白了我的意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天启者的力量激活，“丧钟”开始转动。卜卜也没有使用镜爻保护我——这么近的距离下，攻击的任务就交给卜卜了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "取得胜势的手段是消耗罗赞储存的泰坦力量，而最终的战果既不在我，也不在罗赞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而在于爱思特、猫汐尔、卜卜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "击败、俘虏爱思特，要比击败罗赞简单得多。失去爱思特，罗赞将完全陷入一打三的被动局面。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "重创卜卜和猫汐尔则会破坏“丧钟”的作战体系。对罗赞来说，她们两个也远比我好应对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以，这蓄势待发的一击，我决定用给爱思特。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使“丧钟”即将发动，我也要尝试这么做。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "双腿蹬地，拧腰翻胯。右拳像出膛的炮弹，正中爱思特的拳头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "竹子一样的触感，轻松地透了过去。然后是肩膀——她甚至没能削弱半分拳头上的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“盾牌”被轻易击穿了，露出后面的罗赞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "问题被抛回了罗赞身上——面对即将到来的丧钟和我的攻击，是否要使用泰坦物质？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "爱思特已经失去了战斗力，落在对面的墙边上。在我身后，卜卜随时准备配合“丧钟”发起攻击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "罗赞",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_rozan_03",
        "zh_CN": "呵……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在看到罗赞表情的那一刻，我就知道了罗赞想要干嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "第一次，运用着泰坦力量的两个人硬碰硬地撞在了一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在碰撞发生的一瞬间，“丧钟”的振荡波也如期而至。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "体内的能量态泰坦物质开始向物质态回归，形成同频锁。原本容纳、利用着能量的细胞，在这股粗暴的变化中破碎。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "眼前的一切都红了起来。感觉像是血液结了冰又碎裂，锐利的冰刺在血管内流淌似的，脏器里也好像长出了利刃和锯齿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对面的罗赞双眼血红却又面露狞笑。“丧钟”的下一次振荡波蓄势待发，她竟然强顶着同频锁的控制举起了右拳——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "喀嚓——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "关键时刻，一道身影从我旁边疾驰而过，一阵沉闷而清晰的骨骼碎裂声传了过来——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞破釜沉舟的攻击被切入战局的卜卜瞬间打断，她一记铁山靠把前扑的罗赞撞得反方向飞了出去！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_girl020_02",
        "zh_CN": "哈！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随着一声发力的清啸声，卜卜倾身向前，以猛虎下山之势扑住罗赞，又是一肘，正顶在罗赞心脏的位置！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接着便是疾风骤雨般的连击。飞在空中的罗赞无处借力，加上硬顶了“丧钟”，此时竟被卜卜打得完全着不了地！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗡——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最后一次“丧钟”发动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜终于追不上罗赞的速度了。在确认无法继续追击的瞬间，卜卜双臂架开了罗赞的防御，血肉模糊的胸口敞开在卜卜面前，而卜卜已经掏出了双枪——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哒哒哒哒哒——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "装载了对泰坦物质具有特殊杀伤效果的子弹倾泻而出，强劲的停止力把罗赞的身体钉死在墙上，直到弹匣打空。卜卜继续向前追击，势要在这里结果罗赞——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔莲驱",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_girl012_02",
        "zh_CN": "呃——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔的声音从身后传来，她已经到达极限了。来不及查看她的情况。顶着浑身上下的麻木感，我向罗赞的方向冲了过去——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我距离罗赞只有五米，卜卜距离罗赞也只剩下两米的距离。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肉眼可见的，罗赞已经被轰得稀烂的胸口，开始愈合。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "超过卜卜，举起右拳。能听见罗赞的心脏重新开始跳动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "垫步，蓄力，出拳——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一只手从涤荡的尘埃中伸出，精准地接住了手掌。拳头抵着手掌，直到胸口才停下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的胸骨甚至还裸露在空气中——掺着灰白色泰坦物质的胸骨，血肉从中蔓延。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果再快上一秒……甚至半秒，我就能结果掉她的性命。但即使是这样致命的伤势，她还是恢复过来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗡——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "出乎意料的，第四次“丧钟”到了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔明明已经到极限了。拼命压制住回头的冲动——我明白，这是猫汐尔为杀掉罗赞所压上的最后一道砝码。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "正要蓄起必杀的一拳时，我看见了罗赞的表情——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "面对这最后一次、最关键的一次催命的“丧钟”，罗赞的表情很平静。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在视线的角落，她的另一只手正扣在爱思特头上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "巨量的泰坦物质从爱思特的身上被抽取出来，甚至渗出皮肤、隔空飞向罗赞的心脏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在振荡波命中罗赞之前，浓郁的泰坦物质已经沿着手臂，包裹住了她的左胸和头颅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞被振荡波命中的身体发出沉闷的爆破声。可是，在重重保护之下，在同频锁同样对我产生影响的前提下，已经没有办法利用这个时机杀死罗赞了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随后，停滞的泰坦物质又流动起来，重塑着罗赞的身体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "顶着最后一次“丧钟”的影响，我下了命令。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "撤退！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "闪身抓起昏迷不醒的爱思特，卜卜搀起虚弱的猫汐尔，随着我向与罗赞相反的方向跑去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "背后传来巨大的声响。我回过头，只看见一个两层楼高的怪物正从原地站起来，疗养中心的墙壁在她面前也像是纸糊的玩具一样——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "轰！！！！！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大厅的天花板连着墙壁一起被破坏，露出外面的天空。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "拉开一定距离之后，我看了看猫汐尔的状况。她嘴唇发白，面色发紫，基本完全丧失了战斗的能力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再看身后，怪物——此时能看出罗赞的面容——长着四条手臂，浑身上下都被泰坦物质包裹着，随着呼吸起伏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不像是泰坦，也不像是人类，像是一种泰坦物质和生命结合的、新的生命形态。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "完全想不到战胜的办法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "突然间，一股尖锐的刺痛从脑中传来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜灵鉴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc34ep5_girl020_03",
        "zh_CN": "呕——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 118,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜也在同一时间受到了某种刺激。她扶着墙，止不住地干呕。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 119,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有什么东西来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 120,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "先甩掉罗赞……她追过来了。快！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
